# Performance Rules

Apply these rules when modifying hot paths (agent loop, provider calls, memory queries, gateway request handling).

- Read `docs/standards/engineering/performance.md` for hard limits.
- Read `docs/standards/engineering/performance-testing.md` for measurement methodology.
- Binary size budget: ~1696 KB release. Measure impact of changes with `size build-release/human`.
- Startup time budget: <30 ms. No lazy initialization that blocks startup.
- Peak RSS budget: ~5.7 MB. No unnecessary heap allocations in the hot path.
- Animate only compositor properties in UI (transform, opacity, filter).
- Use `arena` allocator for per-turn allocations that can be bulk-freed.
- Profile before optimizing — measure, don't guess.
